    "Building on these works, [160], [161] extended Stackelberg game-based FL incentive mechanisms to model interactions in edge networks.",
    "The server acts as a leader offering a reward, motivating clients to perform more FL training rounds to improve model accuracy.",
    "[162] criticized existing incentive schemes for privacy burdens on the FL server.",
    "They proposed a twostage Stackelberg game to ensure privacy with a specialized budget.",
    "Users can strive towards optimizing utility under a given privacy budget."
